r \"The Matrix\". Also included is the companion piece \"The Matrix Revisited\" and the best-selling \"The Animatrix\", plus brand-new supplemental materials that encompass every aspect of the \"Matrix\" universe, including two new audio commentaries on each film, \"Enter the Matrix\" video game footage, 106 deep-delving featurettes/documentaries and much more. \"The Matrix\" - Set in the 22nd century, \"The Matrix\" tells of a computer hacker (Reeves) who joins a group of underground insurgents fighting the vast and powerful computers who now rule the earth. The computers are powered by human beings... \"The Matrix Reloaded\" - Sentinel swarm. Smith clones. Neo flies...but perhaps not even a Chosen One gifted with astonishing new powers can stop the advance of the Machines. Neo. Morpeus. Trinity. They\'re back for the powerful second chapter of \"The Matrix\" trilogy, and exciting new allies join them in the struggles against foes who are cloned, ungraded and closing in on humanity\'s last enclave. Back, too, are Wachowski Brothers and producer Joel Silver, expanding their vision with a spectacle that rocks the senses, probes the hart and shapes filmmaking\'s tomorrows. What is \"The Matrix?\" The question is not yet fully answered. And it leads to another: Who created The Matrix? The answers lead to more worlds of bold possibly - and to a destiny that passes from revelations to Revolutions. \"The Matrix Revolutions\" - Provocative Futuristic Action Thriller. \"The Matrix Revolutions\" marks the final explosive chapter in the \"Matrix\" trilogy. \"The Animatrix\" - Welcome to The \"Animatrix,\" a visionary fusion of CG-animation and Japanese anime from the world\'s most revered anime directors. Experience the prequel to \"The Matrix\" and learn about the last cities of mankind, the war with the machines and humanity\'s ultimate downfall. Witness the Final Flight of the Osiris, which sets the stage for \"The Matrix Reloaded\" movie and Enter the Matrix video game. Grasp a more complete understanding of \"The Matrix\" available nowhere else. Expand your mind even further as you unlock a dazzling arsenal of Bonus Materials. It\'s time to plug in.\r\n\r\nCollectible Booklet, Documentary, Featurette.','on','on','on','a:1:{i:1;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Screen Aspect\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"11\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Blu-Ray\";s:6:\"linked\";s:3:\"off\";}i:1;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"12\";s:4:\"name\";s:3:\"DVD\";s:6:\"linked\";s:3:\"off\";}}}}','2009-10-13 14:42:14','2009-10-19 13:09:09','',0,'publish','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(82,'Heart Photo Pendant','heart-photo-pendant','','What a wonderful way to keep dear ones close to your heart. Upload your digital image through our website and we will reproduce it on your choice of either our heart or dog tag style pendant.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pendants are crafted with solid stainless steel backing and hang from an 18\'\' sterling silver ball chain.</li>\r\n<li>We engrave the back with any 3 line message up to 11 characters, per line.</li>\r\n<li>Heart measures 1 1D2 H x 1D2\'\'H.</li>\r\n</ul>','on','off','off','a:0:{}','2009-10-13 14:45:52','2009-10-13 14:45:52','',0,'publish','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(83,'Personalized Nameplate Necklace','personalized-nameplate-necklace','','Chic and stylish, the perfect gift created just for her! Create a beautiful scripted name of your choice in sterling silver, 18kt gold over sterling or 10kt gold.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Personalized nameplate necklace in sterling silver, 18kt gold over sterling silver or 10kt gold</li>\r\n<li>Create the name of your choosing, up to 12 letters long</li>\r\n<li>Comes with attached 18\" chain</li>\r\n<li>Only first letter will be capitalized</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n**Name Input**','on','off','on','a:1:{i:1;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"Finish\";s:7:\"options\";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Sterling Silver\";s:6:\"linked\";s:3:\"off\";}i:1;a:3:{s:2:\"id\"